### Perform Comprehensive Codebase Analysis with Multiple Schemas

Source: https://context7.com/anthropics/claude-agent-sdk-typescript/llms.txt

Defines a complex Zod schema for security, performance, and test coverage analysis. Processes structured output containing arrays of security issues with severity levels, performance metrics, and test coverage percentages with detailed reporting.

```typescript
const AnalysisSchema = z.object({
  security_issues: z.array(z.object({
    severity: z.enum(["critical", "high", "medium", "low"]),
    description: z.string(),
    file_path: z.string(),
    line_number: z.number().optional(),
    recommendation: z.string()
  })),
  performance_metrics: z.object({
    avg_response_time_ms: z.number(),
    memory_usage_mb: z.number(),
    bottlenecks: z.array(z.string())
  }),
  test_coverage: z.object({
    percentage: z.number().min(0).max(100),
    uncovered_files: z.array(z.string()),
    critical_paths_covered: z.boolean()
  })
});

const analysisResponse = query({
  prompt: "Perform comprehensive security, performance, and test coverage analysis",
  options: {
    model: "claude-sonnet-4-5",
    structuredOutput: {
      schema: AnalysisSchema,
      name: "codebase_analysis"
    }
  }
});

for await (const message of analysisResponse) {
  if (message.type === 'structured_output') {
    const analysis = message.data;

    // Process security issues
    console.log(`Found ${analysis.security_issues.length} security issues`);
    analysis.security_issues.forEach(issue => {
      console.log(`[${issue.severity}] ${issue.description}`);
      console.log(`  Location: ${issue.file_path}:${issue.line_number || 'N/A'}`);
      console.log(`  Fix: ${issue.recommendation}`);
    });

    // Review performance metrics
    console.log(`Average response time: ${analysis.performance_metrics.avg_response_time_ms}ms`);
    console.log(`Memory usage: ${analysis.performance_metrics.memory_usage_mb}MB`);

    // Check test coverage
    console.log(`Test coverage: ${analysis.test_coverage.percentage}%`);
    console.log(`Critical paths covered: ${analysis.test_coverage.critical_paths_covered}`);
  }
}
```

